import org.apache.jorphan.collections.HashTree;
import org.apache.jmeter.testelement.TestElement;
import org.apache.jorphan.collections.ForeignKey;
import org.apache.jorphan.collections.ListedHashTree;
import org.apache.jorphan.collections.MapCollection;
import org.apache.jorphan.collections.ShallowCopy;
import org.apache.jorphan.logging.LoggingManager;
import org.apache.jorphan.reflect.ClassFinder;
import org.apache.log.Logger;

import java.util.*;

public class CustomJMeterPlugin {
    private static final Logger log = LoggingManager.getLoggerForClass();

    public void registerNonTestElement() {
        MenuFactory.addNonValidatingTestElementToMenu(SubMenu.class, "/some/path");
    }

    // 自定义元素的类
    public class SubMenu extends TestElement {
        // 实现相关的方法等
    }

    // 必须的静态初始化代码以确保JMeter初始化时注册插件
    static {
        new CustomJMeterPlugin().registerNonTestElement();
    }
}
```

关键点在于 `MenuFactory.addNonValidatingTestElementToMenu` 方法是用于添加非测试类型的 TestElement 到菜单中，因此上面示例中的 `SubMenu` 类可以任何非测试元素，例如帮助、配置等。

如果您关注的是非验证测试元素——比如配置或帮助菜单，而不仅仅是在测试计划中直接作为测试元件，上述的`addNonValidatingTestElementToMenu` 或是结合`TestElement`子类的注册实现是推荐的方式。

To read a CDF (Common Data Format) file in ROOT, you would not use ROOT's built-in functionality directly, as ROOT is primarily designed to handle its own file formats such as ROOT files (.root) and some basic text formats. However, you can still read CDF files in a ROOT environment by using an external library such as `CDFLib`, and then interfacing this library within your ROOT application.

